metadata.name: Genesis Kong #1
metadata.description: **Join the movement here:** ***https://cyberkongz.shop.*** CyberKongz Genesis stands among the most highly valued and coveted NFT collections. The ten “legendary” Kongz command millions of dollars on the rare occasion when they are sold. Even “floor” CyberKongz sell for well over $500,000 dollars. This first and only public minting is your opportunity to own Genesis CyberKongz Pixelated, including both “Legendary” and “OG” Kongz. Mint before they’re gone! Sell, trade, or collect, and watch their value grow during this era of rapid metaverse expansion. Every NFT in this collection has been carefully pixelated using AI-technology. Only one minting is available for each of the 1,000 Genesis CyberKongz, with each owner receiving an individual ERC-721 token with proof of ownership on the Ethereum blockchain. BONUS: Each mint of Genesis CyberKongz Pixelated will be eligible for a free future drop of the next collection in the CyberKongz series: Baby CyberKongz Pixelated.
